snippet.title: Fangame Showcase: Super Mario Prostate Exam (Spritanium)
snippet.description:
Download links at: http://mfgg.taloncrossing.com/index.php?showtopic=218992

This is a demo of a Mario fangame by Spritanium of Mario Fan Games Galaxy (MFGG).

The concept behind this fangame: Mario must evade Luigi's evil probing finger.

While playing, I discovered some hilarious glitches. Again, this is a demo, so it's not a big deal.

Also, do not judge this game by its title. It's not a perverted game. The worst the game has is some suggestive dialogue by the Toads, and that's all. Going by ESRB standards, this game would receive a E-10 rating because of the suggestive content.
